description:
Season Six Match
BELLA ROSSI
The Annihilator
HT: 5'5
WT: 155lbs
Season record (2-0)
Lifetime record (2-0)
Ranked 8th
YANA JORDAN
The Wildcat
HT: 5'6
WT: 135lbs
Season record (1-0)
Lifetime record (1-0)
Ranked 12th
Bella Rossi has crushed her first two opponents and is currently ranked 8th. She has not faced any serious competition... until today. Is she just big and strong, or does she have any skill?
Yana Jordan (ranked 12th) won her first match against a rookie. She comes with a lot of experience from another site, and is technically strong.
Today we will find out just where these two wrestlers belong in the scheme of things. Let me just tell you it was a total all out war, and the loser got more then she bargained for!
title: Bella "The Annihilator" Rossi (2-0) vs Yana "The Wildcat" Jordan (1-0)
